Package: meta4diag
Type: Package
Title: Meta-analysis for diagnostic test studies
Version: 1.0.16
Date: 2015-08-19
Author: Jingyi Guo <jingyi.guo@math.ntnu.no> and Andrea Riebler <andrea.riebler@math.ntnu.no>
Maintainer: Jingyi Guo <jingyi.guo@math.ntnu.no> and Andrea Riebler <andrea.riebler@math.ntnu.no>
Description: This package contains functions which allow to perform Bayesian inference analysis for bivariate meta-analysis of diagnostic test studies using integrated nested Laplace approximation. A purpose built graphic user interface is available. The installation of R package INLA is compulsory for successful usage of this package.
License: GPL
Depends: R (>= 2.10), RGtk2, cairoDevice, methods, grid
Suggests: INLA
Additional_repositories http://www.math.ntnu.no/inla/R/testing

